title: The Trendfamous Dunk Shot 1/25: Neil Young, RHoSLC, Paris Hilton, Disney, Ponce De Leon, NBA
itunes:title: The Trendfamous Dunk Shot 1/25: Neil Young, RHoSLC, Paris Hilton, Disney, Ponce De Leon, NBA
description:
In this edition of The Trendfamous Dunk Shot, Jack and Miles discuss Neil Young demanding Spotify remove his music over Joe Rogan, Bravo firing Jenny from RHoSLC, Paris Hilton's bizarre Jimmy Fallon appearance, Disney's 'different approach' to the Seven Dwarfs, Jim Jordan's immigration tweets, Puerto Rico toppling Ponce De Leon's statue ahead of King Felipe's visit, and NBA news.
